No special markup - row one and column one for headings: JFW, Window-Eyes, HPR. 2. Scope attribute on either TH's or TD's - JFW and HPR. 3. Axis attribute on TH's or TD's - JFW. 4. Use TH for headings - JFW and HPR. 5. Headers attribute with id's specifying heading cells - JFW and HPR. 6. abbr attribute on heading cells - JFW and HPR. Jim Accessibility Consulting 512-306-0931 Evaluation of web evaluation tools at http://jimthatcher.com/erx.htm 
